              <h4>You Own Your Listing</h4>
              <p>Your Airbnb account, your reviews, your Superhost status, your guest relationships. If you leave, everything comes with you.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>Transparent Fee Structure</h4>
              <p>One clear management percentage with no hidden charges. No setup fees, no cleaning markups, no supply markups, no vacancy fees.</p>
