          <div class="info-grid" style="margin-top: 0;">
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>Direct Manager Contact</h4>
              <p>A dedicated account manager who knows your property and responds directly. Not a generic inbox or a group chat with other owners.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>Dynamic Pricing Included</h4>
              <p>Professional pricing tools (PriceLabs, Beyond) used to optimize your rates daily. No flat-rate "set it and forget it" approach.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>Professional Photography</h4>
              <p>High-quality listing photos included at no extra charge. Photography is not a premium add-on; it's the baseline for professional management.</p>
