          <div class="info-grid" style="margin-top: 0;">
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>Multi-Platform Distribution</h4>
              <p>Listed on Airbnb, VRBO, and Booking.com simultaneously. More platforms means more visibility and higher occupancy rates.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>Local GTA Presence</h4>
              <p>A team based in the Greater Toronto Area with local cleaners, maintenance contacts, and knowledge of neighborhood-level demand patterns.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>No Startup Costs</h4>
              <p>Commission-only model. The PM earns only when you earn. No upfront investment before you've received your first booking.</p>
            </div>
